# Workspace backup policy: whitelist mode
# Ignore everything by default
*

# Keep git internals
!.gitignore
!.git/

# Keep core identity/context files
!AGENTS.md
!SOUL.md
!USER.md
!IDENTITY.md
!TOOLS.md
!HEARTBEAT.md
!WORKSPACE_DATA_CLASSIFICATION.md

# Keep knowledge/docs
!memory/
!memory/**
!docs/
!docs/**
!skills/
!skills/**
!avatars/
!avatars/*.svg

# If a file is valuable for backup but currently ignored,
# add an explicit exception here like:
# !reports/important-report-2026-02-26.md
